This directory contains:

1.Configuration Files of : postgresql(postgresql.conf,pg_hba.conf) , apache(httpd.conf)
2.Network bridge creating script (network_bridge directory)
3.Script to create qemu instances (qemu_script directory)
4.Sources code , html files , css files , log from all qemu instances

To setup the website :

create qcow files -> turn up the bridge -> run instances using qemu scripts -> install postgresql,apache,kcgi -> replace the configuration files -> copy the source codes to each individual instance -> use sql files to create the database -> use makefile in programs directory to start the website scripts -> now the website is usable.
